attributes.description: The Company is engaged in the manufacturing of bead wire, a high-carbon steel wire utilized in the production of tires. Additionally, the Company produces drawn steel wire, commonly referred to as black wire, which finds applications in various industries such as automobile, construction, and engineering. [1]
